            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Domine Neptune <lb n="2"/>t<expan><ex>i</ex><abbr>b</abbr><ex>i</ex></expan> d<expan><ex>o</ex><abbr>no</abbr></expan> <expan><ex>h</ex><abbr>ominem</abbr></expan> qui <lb n="3"/>|(solidum) involav<supplied reason="lost">it</supplied> Mu<lb break="no" n="4"/>coni et argenti<supplied reason="lost">olo</supplied>s <lb n="5"/>sex <expan><abbr>ide</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> dono nomi<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>a</abbr></expan> <lb n="6"/>qui decepit si mascel si <lb n="7"/>femina si puuer <note>sic</note> si puue<lb break="no" n="8"/>lla <note>sic</note> ideo dono tibi Niske <note>sic</note> <lb n="9"/>et Neptuno vitam vali<lb break="no" n="10"/>tudinem sanguem eius <lb n="11"/>qui conscius fueris <note>sic</note> eius <lb n="12"/>deceptionis animus qui hoc involavit et <lb n="13"/>qui conscius fuerit ut <lb n="14"/>eum decipias furem <lb n="15"/>qui hoc involavit sanguem <lb n="16"/>eiius <note>sic</note> consumas et de<lb break="no" n="17"/>cipias domin<supplied reason="lost">e</supplied> Ne<supplied reason="lost">p</supplied><lb break="no" n="18"/>tune
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Bleitafel. Gebet für Gerechtigkeit.</p>
            </div>
